        public Archangel(java.lang.String pName,
                 java.lang.String pPicture,
                 java.lang.String pPrayer,
                 java.lang.String pMonth,
                 java.lang.String pDay,
                 java.lang.String pPower,
                 java.lang.String pColor,
                 double pSize,
                 java.lang.String pEssence,
                 int pIlluminance)
        It creates an archangel with a respective candle
        post: An archangel has been created.
        Parameters:
        pName - Archangel name. pName != null && pName != "".
        pPicture - Archangel picture. pPicture != null && pPicture != "".
        pPrayer - Archangel prayer. pPrayer != null && pPrayer != "".
        pMonth - Archangel celebration month. pMonth != null && pMonth !="".
        pDay - Archangel celebration day of the month. pDay != null && pDay !="".
        pPower - The power of the archangel. pPower != null && pPower !="".
        pColor - Candle color of the archangel. pColor != null && pColor != "".
        pSize - Size candle of the archangel. pSize > 0.0.
        pEssence - Candle essence of the archangel. pEssence != null && pEssence != "".
        pIlluminance - Candle illuminance of the archangel. pEssence > 0.
